controller

Class CDController

  • java.lang.Object
    • controller.CDController

  • public class CDController
extends java.lang.Object
    CDController is responsible for connecting the listeners in the CD fxml file to variables in the CDCollection class. CDController is also responsible for updating the cd.txt file to be user for the CD fxml's TableView.
    Author:
    Jesus Nieto

      • initialize

        public void initialize()
        initialize initializes the cell's in the TableView to their respective variables in the CDCollection. initialize also pre-populates the TableView with the variables in CD.txt.

      • deleteButtonHandle
